title: Fox Wake Presents | Reed Hansen We Live
description:
Fox invites you to come spend 24hrs with the "Big Chief" Reed Hansen and learn what makes Reed a legend in the making of wake skating .
If you like drifting the ol' el camino on the back roads of Groveland, catching some gators during the night, shooting guns with the boys, or just finding those couple epic winch spots all in one day... Reed is your man.

Directed by:
Ryan Marcus

Edit/Camera:
Ryan Marcus

Additional Cinematography:
BFY productions
Director/Director of Photography: Sean Kilgus
Camera: Tony Augustinack
Camera/Timelapse: Ryan Brien

Music:
Legendary Shack Shakers
"Dump Road Yodel"
Agridustrial
